# Styling Guidelines

## Tailwind CSS Usage
- Use Tailwind CSS classes exclusively
- Follow mobile-first responsive design
- Use the `cn()` utility from [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts) for conditional classes
- Maintain consistent spacing and typography

## Design System
- Follow the shadcn/ui design system from [components.json](mdc:src/components.json)
- Use consistent color schemes (black/white primary)
- Implement proper hover states and transitions
- Use proper focus states for accessibility

## Component Styling
- Use Tailwind classes directly in components
- Avoid custom CSS when possible
- Use CSS variables for theming
- Implement proper responsive breakpoints

## Global Styles
- Use [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css) for global styles
- Import Mapbox CSS properly
- Use proper font loading with Next.js
- Implement proper CSS reset and base styles

## Swedish Localization
- Use Swedish text content
- Implement proper RTL support if needed
- Use appropriate Swedish typography
- Follow Swedish design conventions